      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2443 - Abu Khadijah narrated from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"The one who spends the night alone in the house is a devil; two are a gathering of whisperers; and three bring companionship.\""
